18-34) in Feerrott.<br>Star Ruby-from vendor.<br>------------------------------------------------<br>Stien of Ulissa (increases size and power of a summoned Water Elementals above level 34) requires:<br><br>Mermaid scale-Sirens on the spires in OOT<br>Ice Giant Toes-Ice Giants in Everfrost Peaks or from Gornit. <br>Stien-Magicians in Najena and Alligators in Feerrott, Magicians (level 9 -24) and Alligators (level 18-34). <br>Sapphire-from vendor. <br><br>[these notes were gathered from my experience and other posts, thank you for your help you know who you are]<br>&nbsp;<br>The Doctor of Agony and Jester of many servers!</td></tr>
